's%20publisher%20convinced%20him%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BHypnotize%26quot%3B%20demo%20in%20late%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20when%20that%20thing%20came%20on%E2%80%A6%20that%20was%20it%2C%20I'm%20done.%20It's%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%20%26quot%3BI%20played%20that%20cassette%20over%20and%20over.%20I%20must've%20played%20it%20for%20half%20an%20hour%2C%2045%20minutes.%20I%20said%2C%20'That's%20a%20fucking%20hit%20record.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20this%20day%2020%20years%20later%E2%80%A6%20like%2C%20I%20ask%20my%20twin%2017-year-olds%2C%20and%20those%2017-year-olds%20were%20not%20born%20when%20'Hypnotize'%20came%20out%2C%20and%20were%20certainly%20not%20born%20when%20'Rise'%20came%20out.%20But%20them%20and%20their%20friends%20love%20that%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20Randy%20added.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20artists%20that%20work%20through%20generations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E20.%20'I'll%20Be%20Missing%20You'%20by%20Diddy%20featuring%20Faith%20Evans%20%26amp%3B%20112%20(1997)%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20he%20leveraged%20his%20fame%20to%20build%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-jay-z-and-diddy-made-millions-off-of-cheap-alcohol-zack-omalley-greenburg-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebusiness%20empire%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sean%20Combs%20(then%20known%20as%20Diddy)%20dominated%20the%20charts%20in%20the%20'90s%20and%20early%202000s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201997%20alone%2C%20Combs%20notched%20three%20No.%201%20hits%20on%20the%20Hot%20100%3A%20%26quot%3BCan't%20Nobody%20Hold%20Me%20Down%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMo%20Money%20Mo%20Problems%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BI'll%20Be%20Missing%20You%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20tribute%20to%20his%20labelmate%2C%20Christopher%20%26quot%3BThe%20Notorious%20B.I.G.%26quot%3B%20Wallace%2C%20who%20was%20murdered%20in%20March%20of%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heartfelt%20single%20reigned%20atop%20the%20chart%20for%2011%20weeks%2C%20whic