E%3Ch2%3EYour%20buffet%20table%20is%20probably%20too%20full%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20have%20buffet%20tables%20in%20their%20dining%20rooms%2C%20both%20to%20act%20as%20a%20place%20to%20serve%20food%20and%20for%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Brent%20said%20she%20often%20finds%20that%20people%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20function%20of%20buffet%20tables%2C%20putting%20too%20many%20knickknacks%20and%20decor%20items%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20they%20overstyle%20them%2C%20and%20then%20when%20you're%20actually%20eating%2C%20you're%20like%2C%20'I%20don't%20have%20anywhere%20for%20food%20or%20the%20servewear%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20common%20because%20we%20just%20want%20it%20to%20look%20good%2C%20but%20then%20we're%20like%2C%20'Oh%20my%20gosh%2C%20I'm%20burning%20my%20hands%20with%20this%20pie.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222105%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dining%20room%20with%20a%20table%20and%20a%20buffet%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7b8a7a3c8094d5dd3a26%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221579%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20buffet%20table%20shouldn't%20be%20overcrowded.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Keeble%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20recommends%20only%20decorating%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20buffet%20table%20to%20ensure%20it's%20as%20functional%20as%20it%20is%20decorative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeave%20a%20third%20of%20it%20open%20so%20that%20you%20have%20a%20practical%20place%20to%20put%20things%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20find%20yourself%20buying%20too%20much%20decor%20generally%2C%20Brent%20says%20%26quot%3Bdelaying%20gratification%26quot%3B%20can%20help%20you%20cut%20back%20on%20buying%20knickknacks%20you%20don't%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20go%20shopping%20and%20instead%20of%20buying%20anything%2C%20I%20say%20to%20myself%2C%20'If%20I%20remember%20that%20I%20want%20this%20in%20seven%20days%2C%20I%20can%20come%20back%20and%20get%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BDelaying%20gratification%20is%20really%2C%20really%20important.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20splurge%20on%20your%20dining%20room%20chairs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20table%20and%20its%20accompanying%20chairs%20are%20typically%20the%20focal%20point%20of%20your%20dining%20room%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20for%20them%20to%20have%20aesthetic%20appeal.%20But%20Brent%20said%20it's%20probably%20not%20worth%20it%20to%20splurge%20on%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fwoman-realized-how-painful-ending-marriage-was-after-selling-table-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edining%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20chairs%20if%20you%20don't%20use%20your%20dining%20room%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20spend%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20dining%20chairs%2C%26quot%3B%20Brent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dining%20room%20with%20one%20chair%20pulled%20out.%20A%20green%20arrow%20points%20to%20the%20chair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7be20ec98e92f74fb4b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20splurge%20on%20chairs.%3Cp%3Eimaginima%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20work%20with%20clients%2C%20that's%20something%20that's%20always%20a%20real%20high-ticket%20item%2C%20and%20in%20reality%2C%20most%20of%20us%20either%20eat%20at%20the%20kitchen%20island%20or%20in%20front%20of%20the%20TV%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20either%20of%20those%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20you%20probably%20won't%20use%20them%20daily%2C%20Brent%20doesn't%20advise%20spending%20a%20lot%20on%20your%20dining%20room%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnless%20