Already%20over%2018%2C700%20Palestinians%20are%20dead%20and%2050%2C500%20injured%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Hamas-run%20Health%20Ministry%2C%20and%20roughly%2090%25%20of%20the%20population%20have%20fled%20their%20homes%20and%20face%20food%20shortages%2C%20no%20electricity%2C%20sanitation%20problems%20in%20overcrowded%20homes%20and%20shelters%2C%20and%20spreading%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20society%20has%20mobilized%20to%20support%20the%20war%20and%20is%20largely%20united%20in%20the%20conviction%20that%20Hamas%2C%20the%20terror%20group%20that%20launched%20a%20murderous%20rampage%20from%20Gaza%20on%20October%207%2C%20must%20never%20again%20be%20allowed%20to%20threaten%20Israel.%20That%20paramount%20goal%20justifies%20and%20necessitates%20the%20use%20of%20maximum%20force.%20If%20Israeli%20leaders%20have%20a%20theory%20of%20what%20comes%20after%2C%20it%20is%20that%20Israel's%20retaliatory%20fury%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20wrecking%20ball%20to%20create%20the%20rubble%20from%20which%20a%20new%20social%20and%20political%20order%20in%20Gaza%20can%20arise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20few%20signs%20Israel%20can%20achieve%20anything%20like%20this%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20chorus%20of%20international%20leaders%20and%20military%20experts%20are%20warning%20that%20Israel%20is%20pursuing%20a%20half-baked%20strategy%20that%20is%20forged%20from%20a%20national%20trauma%20and%20premised%20on%20a%20flawed%20assumption%20%E2%80%94%20that%20massive%20air%20power%20and%20ground%20battles%20can%20defeat%20a%20militancy%20that%20blends%20into%20the%20population.%20In%20fact%2C%20these%20experts%20say%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20likely%20that%20these%20tactics%20will%20simply%20create%20more%20enemy%20combatants%20and%20play%20directly%20into%20Hamas'%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHamas'%20%26quot%3Bvery%20identity%20is%20based%20on%20the%20destruction%20of%20Israel%20and%20not%20working%20with%20Israel%2C%20so%20the%20notion%20that%20collective%20punishment%20is%20going%20to%20convince%20the%20population%20of%20Gaza%20to%20push%20Hamas%20to%20come%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table%20with%20Israel%20is%20just%20not%20going%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Poast%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Chicago%20professor%20specializing%20in%20international%20security.%20%26quot%3BIf%20anything%2C%20they're%20able%20to%20use%20these%20very%20actions%20to%20say%2C%20'Look%2C%20this%20is%20who%20we're%20dealing%20with.%20We're%20dealing%20with%20Israel.%20We've%20long%20told%20you%20that%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20you%20as%20people%2C%20and%20look.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20response%20to%20Hamas'%20barbaric%20attacks%2C%20the%20IDF%20is%20operating%20to%20dismantle%20Hamas%20military%20and%20administrative%20capabilities.%20In%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Hamas'%20intentional%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%2C%20the%20IDF%20follows%20international%20law%20and%20takes%20feasible%20precautions%20to%20mitigate%20civilian%20harm.%26quot%3B%20The%20IDF%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.il%2Fen%2FDepartments%2FGeneral%2Fswords-of-iron-faq-6-dec-2023%232%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20elevated%20level%20of%20Palestinian%20casualties%20are%20due%20to%20Hamas%20using%20them%20as%20human%20shields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20Israel's%20efforts%20are%20not%20bearing%20much%20fruit.%20Hamas's%20top%20leaders%20remain%20at%20large%2C%20hiding%20in%20their%20extensive%20tunnels%20or%20among%20the%201.9%20million%20refugees%20who%20have%20fled%20the%20violence.%20Israel's%20military%20estimates%20it%20has%20killed%205%2C000%20Hamas%20militants%2C%20or%20just%20about%2016%25%20of%20Hamas'%20armed%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hamas-war-news-12-13-2023-10a0370b7b320d73def6b6a2a137f16a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20continue%20to%20the%20end%26quot%3B%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20day%20it%20was%20disclosed%20that%20nine%20Israeli%20troops%20died%20in%20an%20urban%20ambush%3B%20the%20IDF%20has%20lost%20at%20least%20444%20troops%20in%20the%2010%2F7%20attacks%20and%20the%20ground%20invasion.%20Israel's%20defense%20minister%20said%20Thursday%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20destroy%26quot%3B%20Hamas'%20infrastructure%20and%20that%20Israel%20needs%20months%20more%20for%20its%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20US'%20most%20influential%20former%20diplomats%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20believes%20the%20conflict%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20for%20at%20least%20three%20to%20four%20more%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20certain%20tension%20in%20objectives%20even%20from%20our%20own%20standpoint%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20Ambassador%20Dennis%20Ross%2C%20the%20lead%20envoy%20for%20peace%20negotiations%20in%20two%20US%20administrations%2C%20in%20a%20Tuesday%20phone%20call%20from%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20we%20want%20the%20Israelis%20to%20get%20this%20over%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20we%20want%20them%20to%20limit%20the%20way%20that%20they're%20doing%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20military%20destruction%20of%20Hamas%20is%20achievable%2C%20Ross%20told%20BI%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20Israelis%20are%20going%20to%20do%20it%2C%20period.%20And%20in%20the%20end%2C%20whether%20they%20will%20do%20it%20on%20a%20timeline%20that%20we%20want%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20know%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestinians%20stand%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20crater%20after%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Rafah%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20December%203%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b77a20ec98e92f74fb2aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPalestinians%20stand%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20crater%20after%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20in%20Rafah%20in%20the%20southern%20Gaza%20Strip%20on%20December%203%2C%202023.%3Cp%3ESaid%20Khatib%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20bombing%20'trap'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20leaders%20frequently%20use%20World%20War%20II%2C%20which%20saw%20massive%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20bombing%20campaigns%20against%20large%20cities%20like%20Dresden%2C%20Berlin%20and%20Toyko%2C%20as%20a%20reference%20point%20in%20justifying%20a%20bombing%20campaign%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynetnews.com%2Farticle%2Fr1mjsi7ua%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%3C%2Fa%3E%2022%2C000%20targets%20in%20the%20war's%20first%20two%20months.%20Historians%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20bombing%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20the%20practice%20of%20systematically%20striking%20a%20nation's%20economy%20and%20urban%20areas%20to%20try%20to%20damage%20its%20ability%20to%20wage%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetanyahu's%20office%20said%20in%20late%20October%20that%20accepting%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20Hamas%20was%20akin%20to%20the%20US's%20refusal%20to%20do%20so%20%26quot%3Bafter%20the%20bombing%20of%20Pearl%20Harbor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20surprise%201941%20attack%20by%20Imperial%20Japan%20that%20plunged%20America%20into%20war.%20Similarly%2C%20Netanyahu%20parried%20questions%20about%20rising%20civilian%20deaths%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F11%2F01%2Fisrael-historical-comparison-world-war-two-ii%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereferencing%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20WWII%20British%20raid%20that%20bombed%20a%20school%20in%20Nazi-occupied%20Copenhagen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20appears%20to%20have%20gotten%20similar%20treatment.%20He%20said%20Netanyahu%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fbiden-israel-starting-lose-support-over-indiscriminate-bombing-gaza-2023-12-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20in%20a%20private%20discussion%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20carpet%20bombed%20Germany%2C%20you%20dropped%20the%20atom%20bomb%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20civilians%20died.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20conducted%20the%20massacre%20in%20a%20way%20that%20even%20the%20Nazis%20did%20not%20allow%20themselves%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Israeli%20ambassador%20Ido%20Aharoni%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20phone%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Nazis%20were%20trying%20to%20hide%20their%20crimes.%20We%20don't%20have%20footage%20of%20Jews%20dying%20in%20the%20gas%20chambers%2C%20but%20Hamas%20did%20it%20enthusiastically%2C%20and%20they%20recorded%20themselves%20and%20they%20shared%20it%20with%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAharoni%2C%20a%20career%20diplomat%20who%20is%20now%20a%20senior%20faculty%20member%20at%20Tel%20Aviv%20University%2C%20said%20that%20Israel%20must%20use%20its%20full%20force%20to%20shatter%20Hamas%20so%20it%20can%20never%20again%20threaten%20Israel%2C%20and%20if%20this%20imperative%20requires%20leveling%20swaths%20of%20Gaza%20and%20straining%20the%20access%20of%20its%20two%20million%20residents%20to%20food%20and%20water%2C%20then%20that's%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20philosophically%20when%20you%20deal%20with%20an%20enemy%20that%20doesn't%20value%20life%3F%20It's%20a%20big%20philosophical%20debate.%20So%2010%2F7%20helped%20us%20to%20rewrite%20the%20rules%20of%20how%20we%20fight%20Hamas.%20And%20we%20made%20a%20decision%20in%20this%20philosophical%20debate%20that%20we%20need%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20take%20them%20out.%20And%20if%20the%20collateral%20damage%20is%20going%20to%20be%20dramatic%2C%20just%20as%20the%20collateral%20damage%20in%20Germany%20and%20just%20the%20collateral%20damage%20in%20Japan%20was%20dramatic%2C%20then%20so%20be%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAharoni%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20unreasonable%20to%20expect%20Israel%20to%20go%20to%20war%20and%20expect%20Israel%20not%20to%20win%20the%20war%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20Troops%20of%20the%203rd%20Armored%20Division%2C%201st%20U.S.%20Army%2C%20advance%20through%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Cologne%2C%20Germany%20on%20Mar.%208%2C%201945.%20Cologne%20was%20one%20of%20the%20German%20cities%20the%20Allies%20targeted%20in%20their%20strategic%20bombing%20campaign.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657b7c4750edbc52a864798f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222325%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EU.S.%20Troops%20of%20the%203rd%20Armored%20Division%2C%201st%20U.S.%20Army%2C%20advance%20through%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20city%20of%20Cologne%2C%20Germany%20on%20Mar.%208%2C%201945.%20Cologne%20was%20one%20of%20the%20German%20cities%20the%20Allies%20targeted%20in%20their%20strategic%20bombing%20campaign.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bombing%20campaign%20against%20Hamas-run%20Gaza%20is%20on%20pace%20proportionally%20with%20the%20destruction%20delivered%20in%20the%20strategic%20bombing%20of%20Nazi%20Germany.%20Yet%20our%20collective%20hazy%20memories%20of%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BGood%20War%26quot%3B%20may%20obscure%20the%20fact%20that%2C%20at%20best%2C%20the%20Allied%20strategic%20bombing%20of%20Germany%20didn't%20work%20%E2%80%94%20it%20likely%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20more%20Allied%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20fallacy%20of%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bbomb%20the%20shit%20out%20of%20them%26quot%3B%20approach%20is%20that%20enough%20death%20and%20destruction%20creates%20a%20breaking%20point%20where%20the%20populace%20cracks%20and%20refuses%20to%20support%20its%20government%20or%20overthrows%20it.%20In%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20Allies%20pursued%20a%20devastating%20bombing%20campaign%20against%2092%20cities%20and%20towns%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20fomenting%20dissent%20against%20dictator%20Adolf%20Hitler%20and%20degrading%20Germany's%20will%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20never%20happened%2C%20and%20the%20Wehrmacht%20fought%20hard%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20very%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Robert%20Pape%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Chicago%20professor%20and%20scholar%20of%20military%20power.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20really%20no%20case%20to%20make%20that%20the%20killing%20of%20German%20civilians%20in%20World%20War%20II%20by%20the%20Allied%20bombing%20hastened%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%20It%20did%20not%20produce%20political%20effects%20and%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20it%20stiffened%20the%20morale%20of%20the%20German%20fighters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPape%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BBombing%20to%20Win%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20landmark%20study%20of%2040%20strategic%20bombing%20campaigns%20in%20the%2020th%20Century.%20Pape's%20research%20identified%20what%20he%20called%20an%20air%20power%20%26quot%3Btrap%26quot%3B%20of%20mistaken%20thinking%20by%20military%20leaders%2C%20who%20often%20believe%20massive%20bombardment%20leads%20those%20bombed%20to%20capitulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20bomb%20the%20civilians%2C%20the%20local%20population%20gets%20more%20angry%20and%20more%20fearful%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Pape%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20they're%20fearful%20of%20is%20being%20then%20occupied%20militarily%20by%20this%20country%20and%20military%20force%20that%20bombed%20them%20so%20mercilessly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENazi%20Germany's%20defeat%20may%20also%20be%20instructive%20for%20Israel's%20goal%20of%20a%20post-war%20Gaza%20free%20of%20Hamas%2C%20which%20the%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20has%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Beliminate.%26quot%3B%20The%20military%20defeat%20of%20the%20Nazis%20required%20a%20naval%20blockade%2C%20air%20power%2C%20and%20enormous%20armies%20closing%20in%20on%20Germany%20from%20two%20sides%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20its%20wake%20only%20about%20200%20of%20the%20top%20Nazi%20leaders%20were%20tried%2C%20leaving%20many%20responsible%20for%20atrocities%20untouched.%20Many%20Nazi%20Party%20members%20held%20positions%20of%20authority%20in%20postwar%20Germany%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Finternational%2Fgermany%2Ffrom-dictatorship-to-democracy-the-role-ex-nazis-played-in-early-west-germany-a-810207.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%3C%2Fa%3E%2025%20cabinet%20ministers%20and%20a%20chancellor.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20new%20government%20was%20hardly%20de-Nazified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMassive%20bombardment%20has%20had%20a%20checkered%20track%20record%20in%20the%20wars%20since.%20For%20instance%2C%20Poast%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%20professor%20and%20a%20colleague%20of%20Pape%2C%20said%20Israel's%20campaign%20in%20some%20ways%20resembles%20the%20US's%20expansion%20of%20strategic%20bombing%20into%20Laos%20and%20Cambodia%2C%20which%20ultimately%20failed%20to%20strangle%20North%20Vietnam%20and%20the%20Vietcong's%20supply%20lines%20and%20came%20at%20an%20estimated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Ffrontlineworld%2Fstories%2Fcambodia%2Ftl02.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilian%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20after%20bombing%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20with%20warplanes%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525b10d68f1d46f52adb7e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20after%20bombing%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20with%20warplanes%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%20Another%20munition%20can%20be%20seen%20falling%20toward%20a%20target.%3Cp%3EMomen%20Faiz%2FNurPhoto%20via%20