%20author%20and%20his%20niece%20sitting%20outside.%20There%20is%20a%20brick%20wall%20behind%20them%20and%20it%20is%20sunny%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d17699c7d23cb3b9e6604%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20his%20niece.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20options%20for%20starting%20a%20family%20are%20limited%20and%20expensive%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20have%20deliberated%20over%20our%20options%20to%20start%20a%20family.%20When%20we%20started%20to%20discuss%20having%20a%20child%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20down%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsurrogate-on-journey-and-why-she-wants-keep-doing-it-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20surrogacy%20route%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20one%20of%20us%20would%20be%20the%20biological%20father.%20I%20wanted%20our%20genetic%20legacy%20to%20be%20passed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurrogacy%20is%20a%20complex%20and%20expensive%20process.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20where%20we%20live%2C%20it's%20legal%2C%20but%20surrogacy%20arrangements%20are%20not%20enforceable%20by%20law.%20If%20something%20goes%20wrong%2C%20parents-to-be%20could%20find%20themselves%20in%20a%20sticky%20and%20heartbreaking%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK's%20National%20Health%20Service%20recommends%20that%20those%20considering%20surrogacy%20don't%20do%20it%20independently.%20Many%20organizations%20(like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.surrogacy.org.uk%2Fintended-parents%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ECOTS%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E)%20work%20with%20both%20parties%2C%20offering%20support%2C%20knowledge%2C%20and%20guidance%2C%20to%20make%20the%20process%20smoother%20and%20less%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFactoring%20in%20embryo%20creation%2C%20fertility-clinic%20fees%2C%20and%20surrogate%20expenses%2C%20the%20cost%20can%20amount%20to%20over%20%2437%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20frustrates%20me%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20for%20many%20cis%20straight%20people%20to%20start%20a%20family.%20But%20I%20also%20know%20that%20this%20isn't%20the%20case%20for%20all%20cis%20straight%20people%20and%20that%20many%20are%20also%20going%20through%20turmoil%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20fertility%20and%20family%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20LGBTQ%2B%20people%20like%20us%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20extra%20obstacles.%20Practically%20speaking%2C%20the%20information%20available%20for%20surrogacy%20and%20adoption%20can%20be%20ambiguous%20and%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdoption%20seems%20like%20the%20best%20option%20for%20us%2C%20so%20we're%20starting%20to%20plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20route%20available%20to%20us%20is%20adoption%2C%20and%20we%20think%20it's%20the%20one%20we%20want%20to%20pursue.%20We've%20seen%20friends%20adopt%2C%20and%20despite%20knowing%20how%20long%20and%20arduous%20the%20process%20was%20%E2%80%94%20they%20went%20through%20several%20social%20workers%20and%20had%20their%20lives%20dissected%20%E2%80%94%20we%20feel%20more%20inspired%20now%20that%20they're%20on%20the%20other%20side%20and%20have%20a%20beautiful%20little%20boy.%20For%20us%2C%20it%20also%20just%20makes%20sense%20to%20give%20a%20home%20to%20a%20child%20in%20the%20world%20who%20needs%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20option%20we%20choose%2C%20we%20know%20it%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20easy.%20Perhaps%20we%20just%20need%20to%20stop%20worrying%20about%20the%20obstacles%2C%20accept%20the%20way%20things%20are%2C%20and%20put%20a%20plan%20into%20action%2C%20because%20our%20future%20definitely%20has%20a%20child%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20gotten%20far%20with%20our%20planning%20yet%3B%20we've%20been%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20talking%20about%20what%20we%20want%20and%20feeling%20overwhelmed%20by%20how%20much%20work%20is%20involved.%20Our%20goal%20for%202024%2C%20however%2C%20is%20to%20get%20our%20butts%20into%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20starters%2C%20I%20want%20us%20to%20be%20fully%20informed%20about%20how%20adoption%20works%20and%20how%20it%20would%20work%20for%20us.%20I%20foresee%20lots%20of%20chats%20over%20wine%20with%20our%20friends%20who%20went%20through%20the%20process.%20It%20took%20them%20years%20to%20get%20to%20where%20they%20are%20today%2C%20but%20seeing%20them%20with%20their%20son%20shows%20me%20it's%20worthwhile.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20are%20in%20our%20late%2030s%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it'll%20happen%20for%20us%20before%20we%20turn%2040%2C%20but%20that's%20OK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20parenthood%20may%20be%20further%20in%20the%20future%20than%20we'd%20like%2C%20some%20year%20down%20the%20line%20Halloween%20and%20Christmas%20will%20be%20just%20as%20magical%20for%20us%20as%20they%20are%20for%20many%20other%20families.%20We%20love%20to%20wow%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20when%20we%20dress%20up%20at%20Halloween%2C%20and%20our%20child%20will%20be%20no%20exception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20milk%20and%20cookies%20will%20be%20out%20on%20Christmas%20morning.%20Even%20if%20the%20little%20one%20wakes%20up%20at%203%20a.m.%2C%20we'll%20be%20there%2C%20sharing%20in%20their%20excitement%20%E2%80%94%20but%20hopefully%20not%20every%20year%2C%20because%20Daddy%20needs%20his%20beauty%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-season-difficult-for-queer-couples-who-want-kids-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702726081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655d19784ca513d8242d40ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-season-difficult-for-queer-couples-who-want-kids-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20want%20kids%2C%20and%20the%20holidays%20can%20be%20a