20to%20feel%20like%20something%20might%20be%20off.%20A%20gentleman%20with%20three%20young%20children%20up%20ahead%20of%20us%20was%20waving%20his%20hands%20around%20while%20talking%20to%20the%20gate%20agent.%20He%20looked%20like%20his%20blood%20pressure%20was%20through%20the%20roof.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20approached%2C%20we%20discovered%20what%20all%20the%20fuss%20was%20about.%20%26quot%3BMay%20I%20see%20your%20son's%20birth%20certificate%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20staff%20member%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20confused.%20I%20handed%20over%20my%20son's%20passport%2C%20and%20said%20that%20surely%2C%20that%20had%20to%20be%20enough.%20However%2C%20it%20wasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20needed%20his%20birth%20certificate%20to%20get%20on%20the%20plane%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20explained%20that%20all%20minors%20traveling%20through%20any%20South%20African%20port%20of%20entry%20must%20have%20an%20unabridged%20birth%20certificate%20or%20an%20equivalent%20document%20due%20to%20human%20trafficking%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20stood%20there%20incredulous.%20Tired%20and%20depleted%2C%20we%20stepped%20aside%20with%20the%20other%20family%20and%20waited.%20By%20this%20point%2C%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-board-plane-faster-avoid-delays-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etravel%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20already%20been%20shuffled%20around%2C%20and%20we%20were%20at%20the%20end%20of%20our%20tether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20before%2C%20our%20flight%20from%20Melbourne%2C%20Australia%2C%20to%20Dubai%20had%20been%20diverted%20to%20a%20nearby%20city%20for%20several%20hours%20due%20to%20a%20fog%20weather%20phenomenon%2C%20and%20we'd%20missed%20our%20interconnecting%20flight%20to%20Cape%20Town%2C%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20finally%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Dubai%2C%20we%20waited%20five%20hours%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Faviation-experts-why-its-a-nightmare-to-fly-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20flights%20to%20be%20rebooked%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%20two%20women%20processing%20an%20entire%20flight's%20worth%20of%20new%20bookings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20several%20occasions%2C%20we%20asked%20staff%20members%20for%20water%20for%20our%20toddler%20and%20were%20told%2C%20%26quot%3BSure%2C%20we'll%20be%20right%20back%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%20They%20never%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20our%20flights%20were%20rebooked.%20We%20had%20a%20few%20hours'%20sleep%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20then%20at%201%20am%2C%20we%20made%20our%20way%20back%20to%20the%20airport.%20We%20thought%20our%20ordeal%20was%20finally%20almost%20over%3B%20that's%20when%20we%20were%20asked%20for%20his%20birth%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20panic%2C%20we%20called%20a%20friend%20in%20Australia%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20break%20into%20our%20house%2C%20retrieve%20the%20birth%20certificate%20from%20our%20filing%20cabinet%2C%20and%20send%20us%20a%20scanned%20copy.%20He%20did%20it.%20But%20even%20that%20wasn't%20enough.%20We%20were%20told%20it%20had%20to%20be%20certified%20by%20the%20South%20African%20embassy%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20watched%20miserably%20as%20the%20gate%20closed%20and%20our%20flight%20departed.%20For%20the%20next%2014%20hours%2C%20we%20waited%20in%20the%20transit%20area%20with%20our%20one-year-old%2C%20feeling%20like%20we%20were%20being%20pranked.%20An%20employee%20would%20say%20they%20were%20looking%20into%20our%20case%2C%20only%20to%20walk%20off%20and%20never%20be%20seen%20again.%20It%20felt%20as%20though%20we'd%20never%20get%20out%20of%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20put%20out%20a%20call%20for%20help%2C%20and%20it%20was%20answered%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20desperation%2C%20I%20put%20out%20a%20mayday%20call%20on%20social%20media%20to%20see%20if%20anyone%20could%20help%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20happened%20to%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20an%20airline%20hostess%20living%20in%20Dubai.%20We%20got%20in%20touch