m%20aware%20that%20my%20Art%20Basel%20experience%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20some%20outside%20observer%2C%20isn't%20the%20same%20as%20others%20who%20attended%20the%20festival%20to%20do%20very%20different%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20airport%20heading%20home%2C%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20phone%20tells%20someone%20that%20Art%20Basel%20was%20a%20success.%20I%20assume%20she's%20a%20collector%2C%20but%20find%20out%20she's%20an%20interior%20designer%20who%20picked%20up%20a%20few%20millions'%20worth%20of%20pieces%20for%20her%20clients.%20(That's%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20but%20it's%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.artsy.net%2Farticle%2Fartsy-editorial-sold-art-basel-miami-beach-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20fair's%20top-selling%20piece%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.christies.com%2Fen%2Flot%2Flot-6076405%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3EPhilip%20Guston's%20%26quot%3BPainter%20at%20Night%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20went%20for%20a%20reported%20%2420%20million.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20reminded%20that%20while%20Miami%20throws%20a%20big%20party%20when%20Art%20Basel%20comes%20to%20town%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20business%20meeting%20and%20an%20expensive%20market.%20There%20just%20happens%20to%20be%20an%20art%20fair%20going%20on%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-beach-art-basel-what-its-like-to-visit-photos-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702724221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cbb000ec98e92f75027c0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-beach-art-basel-what-its-like-to-visit-photos-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Art%20Basel%20Miami%20Beach%20turned%2021%20this%20year.%20Business%20Insider's%20reporter%20visite