Justice%20will%20I%20give%20to%20others%20when%20I%20am%20myself%20hopeless%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20her%20letter%2C%20the%20judge%20also%20issued%20a%20message%20to%20working%20women%20in%20the%20country%2C%20warning%20them%20of%20the%20tall%20order%20of%20their%20fight%20against%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wish%20to%20tell%20all%20the%20working%20women%20in%20India%3A%20Learn%20to%20live%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20truth%20of%20our%20lives.%20The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers%E2%80%A6.And%20I%20am%20judge.%20I%20could%20not%20even%20a%20muster%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20for%20myself%2C%20let%20alone%20justice.%20I%20advise%20all%20women%20to%20learn%20to%20be%20a%20toy%2C%20or%20a%20non-living%20thing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702724067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'The%20POSH%20ACT%20is%20a%20big%20wholesome%20lie%20told%20to%20us.%20No%20one%20listens%2C%20no%20one%20bothers...And%20I%20am%20judge.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcivil-judges-letter-cji-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%20General%20Insurance%20launches%20new%20policy%20for%20overseas%20treatment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702723978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-04%2F05%2Ffull%2F1649179134-3732.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-general-insurance-launches-new-policy-for-overseas-treatment-123121600430_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20General%20Insurance%20Company%20Lt