-of-steps-taken-to-secure-places-of-worship-sc-to-manipur-9070194%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20was%20told%20by%20the%20Manipur%20government%20that%20it%20has%20identified%20the%20places%20of%20worship%20that%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20during%20the%20clashes.%20The%20bench%20asked%20the%20government%20to%20provide%20a%20list%20of%20these%20places%20to%20the%20committee%20within%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20all%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20denomination%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20such%20structures%2C%20which%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20should%20be%20identified%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20was%20also%20permitted%20by%20the%20court%20to%20prepare%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20proposal%2C%20including%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20places%20of%20worship%20which%20were%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%E2%80%9D%20and%20extended%20its%20term%20by%20six%20months%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuzefa%20Ahmadi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Meitei%20Christian%20Churches%20Council%2C%20said%20the%20court%20should%20direct%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20make%20arrangements%20so%20that%20Christians%20can%20congregate%20for%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVibha%20Datta%20Makhija%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20committee%2C%20said%20the%20panel%20%E2%80%9Chad%20visited%20and%20found%20that%20religious%20and%20non-religious%20buildings%20have%20suffered%20large%20degree%20of%20damage.%20Religious%20places%20were%20of%20various%20faiths%20including%20some%20Buddhist%20temples.%20Therefore%20we%20had%20asked%20the%20state%20to%20make%20a%20list%20of%20damaged%20places%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20assured%20by%20solicitor%20general%20Tushar%20Mehta%20and%20additional%20solicitor%20general%20Aishwarya%20Bhati%20that%20the%20Manipur%20government%20will%20ensure%20that%20people%20in%20relief%20camps%20can%20participate%20in%20Christmas%20ceremonies.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702718044000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Finform-panel-of-steps-to-secure-places-of-worship-supreme-court-tells-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Details%20of%20all%20places%20of%20worship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20denomination%20and%20the%20nature%20of%20such%20structures%2C%20which%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed%20should%20be%20identified%2C%20the%20court%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Finform-panel-of-steps-to-secure-places-of-worship-supreme-court-tells-manipur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tiger-Kareena%20shoot%20for%20'Singham%20Again'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702717999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106043397%2Cimgsize-57894.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsingham-again-stars-tiger-shroff-and-kareena-kapoor-khan-get-into-action-mode-on-the-film-sets-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F106043343.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106043343.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETiger%20Shroff%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20stars%20of%20Rohit%20Shetty's%20'Singham%20Again'%2C%20were%20spotted%20on%20the%20film%20sets%20for%20a%20late%20night%20shoot%20in%20Mumbai.%20Kareena%2C%20playing%20A