itle%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSon%20Innocent%2C%20Will%20Approach%20Court%26quot%3B%3A%20Parliament%20Breach%20Mastermind's%20Father%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20has%20launched%20a%20massive%20investigation%20into%20the%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20where%20two%20men%20jumped%20into%20the%20House%20and%20released%20coloured%20smoke.%20The%20anti-terror%20cell%20is%20questioning%20five%20accused%20to%20find%20out%20how%20they%20managed%20to%20breach%20the%20high%20level%20of%20security.%20Officials%20believe%20that%20the%20breach%20was%20planned%20by%20a%20Kolkata-based%20teacher%20Lalit%20Jha.%20But%20Jha's%20family%20has%20asserted%20that%20he%20was%20not%20involved%20and%20is%20prepared%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20learned%20about%20the%20incident%20only%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jha's%20father%2C%20Devanand%20Jha%2C%20insisting%20that%20his%20son%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20breach.%20He%20emphasised%20that%20his%20son%20was%20a%20responsible%20citizen%20having%20completed%20his%20bachelor's%20degree%20and%20had%20received%20accolades%20in%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeviating%20from%20the%20version%20presented%20by%20police%20after%20the%20initial%20probe%20Devanand%20Jha%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BLalit%20has%20always%20been%20concerned%20about%20our%20well-being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20confusion%20about%20the%20allegations%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%2032-year-old%20used%20to%20inquire%20only%20about%20their%20welfare.%20%26quot%3BMy%20son%20is%20not%20an%20offender.%20We%20will%20go%20to%20court.%20You%20can%20ask%20the%20villagers%3B%20my%20son%20was%20not%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20Jha's%20mother%20echoed%20the%20sentiment%2C%20describing%20her%20son%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20boy.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20able%20to%20understand.%20We%20had%20no%20information%20about%20this%20