%20you%2C%20Captain%20RO%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20MI%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Mumbai%20Indians%20said%20the%20change%20in%20leadership%20was%20part%20of%20their%20future%20planning%20and%20thanked%20Rohit%20for%20his%20exemplary%20service%20to%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Indians%20are%20the%20most%20successful%20IPL%20franchise%20alongside%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20who%20both%20have%20won%20five%20titles%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20who%20recently%20led%20India%20to%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%2C%20had%20been%20captaining%20the%20franchise%20since%202013%20when%20they%20lifted%20first%20of%20their%20five%20IPL%20trophies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20titles%20under%20Rohit's%20captaincy%20came%20in%202015%2C%202017%2C%202019%20and%202020.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20had%20made%20it%20to%20the%20play-offs%20in%20IPL%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20express%20our%20gratitude%20to%20Rohit%20Sharma%20for%20his%20exceptional%20leadership%3B%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20captain%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%20since%202013%20has%20been%20nothing%20short%20of%20extraordinary%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mahela%20Jayawardene%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F244-mahela-jayawardene-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMahela%20Jayawardene%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20MI's%20Global%20Head%20of%20Performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702716720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Ft41b4ne8_hardik-and-rohit_625x300_15_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Frohit-sharma-informed-about-mumbai-indians-captaincy-change-during-cricket-world-cup-report-4684662%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20new%20report%20has%20claimed%20that%20Rohit%20Sharma%20was%20informed%20about%20the%20need%20of%20change%20in%20Mumbai%20