0praised%20for%20its%20portrayal%20of%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESchindler%E2%80%99s%20List%3C%2Fem%3E%20marked%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20Spielberg%E2%80%99s%20career.%20The%20director%20later%20said%20making%20the%20film%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnofilmschool.com%2Fschindlers-list-american-history%5C%22%3Echanged%20his%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20this%20point%2C%20he%20was%20known%20as%20a%20thrilling%20blockbuster%20director.%20With%20%3Cem%3ESchindler%E2%80%99s%20List%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Spielberg%20turned%20his%20attention%20to%20darker%2C%20conflicted%20characters%20and%20shifted%20his%20focus%20to%20bigger%20themes%20of%20good%20and%20evil%2C%20heroism%20in%20adversity%20and%20the%20human%20cost%20of%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20later%20work%20is%20still%20exciting%20and%20still%20jolts%20the%20senses%20in%20ways%20that%20very%20few%20contemporary%20filmmakers%20can%2C%20as%20in%20the%20musical%20showmanship%20of%20%3Cem%3EWest%20Side%20Story%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2021)%20or%20the%20fantastical%20realism%20of%20%3Cem%3EWar%20Horse%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2011).%20But%20%3Cem%3ESchindler%E2%80%99s%20List%3C%2Fem%3E%20outshines%20them%20all%20with%20its%20detached%20focus%20on%20the%20sheer%20brutality%20and%20its%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20look%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FgG22XNhtnoY%3Fwmode%3Dtransparent%26start%3D0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetelling%20the%20Holocaust%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESchindler%E2%80%99s%20List%3C%2Fem%3E%20tells%20the%20true%20story%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fencyclopedia.ushmm.org%2Fcontent%2Fen%2Farticle%2Foskar-schindler%5C%22%3EOskar%20Schindler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20German%20businessman%20who%20saved%201%2C100%20Jews%20from%20the%20Holo