es%20of%20India.%20Congress%20is%20%23CorruptionKiDukan%20(the%20hub%20of%20corruption).%20Nearly%20%E2%82%B9300%20crore%20recovered%20from%20the%20premises%20of%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Dheeraj%20Sahu%20in%20Jharkhand%20is%20a%20living%20proof%20of%20this.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20denying%20that%20the%20raids%20have%20been%20a%20source%20of%20acute%20embarrassment%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fparty-not-connected-sahu-should-explain-source-of-money-unearthed-congress-on-odisha-i-t-raids-2804462%5C%22%3Eleft%20Sahu%20to%20fend%20for%20himself%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20what%20is%20surprising%20is%20that%20despite%20statements%20from%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20on%20the%20seizure%2C%20the%20MP%20from%20Jharkhand%20has%20not%20been%20arrested.%20He%20only%20reacted%20to%20the%20issue%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcong-mp-dhiraj-sahu-10-day-i-t-raids-end-highest-ever-cash-haul-9070112%2F%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20happening%20today%20makes%20me%20sad.%20I%20can%20admit%20that%20the%20money%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20belongs%20to%20my%20firm%E2%80%A6%20The%20cash%20that%20has%20been%20recovered%20is%20related%20to%20my%20liquor%20firms%2C%20it%20is%20the%20proceedings%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20liquor%E2%80%A6%20This%20money%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20political%20party%20as%20is%20being%20said%E2%80%A6%20The%20money%20is%20not%20all%20mine%2C%20it%20belongs%20to%20my%20family%20and%20other%20related%20firms%E2%80%A6I-T%20has%20raided%20now%2C%20I%20will%20give%20account%20for%20everything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell-known%20political%20analyst%20professor%20Rajar%20Kujur%20finds%20this%20bizarre.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20was%20Sahu%20not%20arrested%3F%20He%20is%20no%20small%20person%20and%20if%20he%20is%20being%20linked%20to%20the%20seized%20cash%20in%20any%20way%2C%20he%20should%20by%20now%20have%20been%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20agency%20and%20his%20statement%20should%20have%20been%20taken.%20That%20may%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20entire%20controversy%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kujur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20laws%20regarding%20economic%20offences%20as%20weak%20and%20liable%20to%20be%20exploited%20by%20influential%20people%20Kujor%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CHad%20the%20laws%20been%20strong%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20irregularities%20that%20the%20IT%20suspects%20the%20Sahu%20family%20to%20have%20carried%20out%20would%20not%20have%20taken%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20reactions%20of%20political%20parties%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThough%20the%20seizure%20of%20cash%20is%20a%20reality%2C%20the%20politics%20over%20it%20is%20distasteful%20and%20allegations%20and%20counter-allegations%20are%20being%20made%20by%20the%20parties%20only%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20next%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20tremors%20in%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20tremors%20of%20the%20raids%20that%20began%20on%20December%206%20and%20lasted%20over%20four%20days%20are%20still%20being%20felt%20in%20Odisha%20from%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20around%20Rs%20350%20crore%20was%20recovered.%20Though%20seizures%20were%20also%20made%20from%20locations%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20major%20recoveries%20were%20made%20from%20Bolangir%2C%20Sambalpur%2C%20Sundergarh%20and%20Bhubaneswar%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20main%20hub%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20also%20triggered%20a%20blame%20game%20among%20the%20major%20political%20parties%20in%20Odisha%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20targeting%20both%20Congress%20and%20the%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD).%20Senior%20saffron%20party%20leaders%20appear%20convinced%20that%20the%20cash%20was%20stashed%20at%20the%20business%20establishments%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%20with%20the%20knowledge%20of%20BJD%20leadership%20and%20would%20have%20been%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20the%20regional%20party%20at%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bulk%20of%20the%20seized%20cash%20was%20recovered%20from%20Bolangir%2C%20which%20is%20known%20to%20be%20a%20poor%20and%20backward%20district.%20The%20money%20was%20obviously%20stashed%20there%20to%20avoid%20suspicion.%20Nobody%20would%20imagine%20such%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20cash%20being%20hidden%20somewhere%20in%20Bolangir.%20The%20ruling%20BJD%2C%20which%20was%20preparing%20for%20early%20elections%2C%20perhaps%20in%20December%2C%20knew%20about%20it%20and%20would%20have%20used%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Loisingha%20MLA%20Mukesh%20Mahaling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahaling%2C%20whose%20constituency%20is%20part%20of%20Bolangir%20district%2C%20alleged%20that%20unscrupulous%20elements%20have%20entered%20the%20liquor%20trade%20in%20the%20state%20with%20the%20government%20turning%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20irregularities.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy%20is%20faulty%20with%20no%20control%20of%20traders.%20Licences%20are%20renewed%20at%20will%20and%20they%20promote%20whoever%20they%20want%20to%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MLA%2C%20who%20is%20convinced%20that%20liquor%20barons%20and%20the%20BJD%20leadership%20are%20working%20hand%20in%20glove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20since%20the%20BJD%20government%20presented%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fodisha-finance-minister-presents-supplementary-budget-of-28200-crore%2Farticle67335018.ece%23%3A%5C%22%3Esupplementary%20budget%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%2C%20during%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20practice%20of%20doing%20so%20in%20the%20winter%20session%2C%20it%20indicated%20that%20the%20party%20wants%20to%20hold%20early%20elections.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20money%20stashed%20away%20by%20%5BSahu%E2%80%99s%20family%5D%20and%20recovered%20by%20the%20IT%20department%20would%20have%20been%20used%20by%20the%20BJD%20in%20the%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20BJD%20MLA%20and%20former%20minister%20Amar%20Satpathy%20rubbished%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20and%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20probe%20into%20the%20issue%2C%20Congress%20veteran%20Ganeshwar%20Behera%20demanded%20a%20completely%20impartial%20inquiry%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20truth.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20law%20should%20take%20its%20course%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20anyone%20found%20guilty%20of%20corruption%20should%20be%20punished.%20But%20for%20the%20whole%20truth%20to%20come%20out%2C%20we%20need%20an%20independent%20inquiry.%20We%20want%20a%20probe%20by%20a%20court-monitored%20SIT.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20trust%20IT%2C%20ED%20or%20CBI%20as%20they%20are%20all%20biased%20and%20act%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20central%20BJP%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Behera.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20vast%20empire%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20IT%20officials%20are%20said%20to%20be%20probing%20deeper%20into%20the%20business%20interests%20of%20the%20Sahu%20family%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20the%20liquor%20business%20for%20several%20decades.%20The%20family%20owns%20the%20BDPL%20group%20which%20comprises%20four%20companies%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20ones%20being%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Private%20Limited%20based%20in%20western%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Boudh%20district%20and%20Baldeo%20Sahu%20Infra%20Private%20Limited%20based%20in%20Bolangir.%20The%20business%20was%20established%20by%20Rai%20Saheb%20Baldeo%20Sahu%2C%20the%20late%20father%20of%20Dhiraj%20Sahu%2C%20and%20today%20has%20country%20liquor%20and%20Indian%20Made%20Foreign%20Liquor%20(IMFL)%20shops%20all%20over%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20the%20group%20dominates%20the%20country%20liquor%20manufacturing%20and%20marketing%20business%20in%20Odisha%20with%20control%20over%20250%20country%20liquor%20units%20in%20the%20western%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20where%20%3Cem%3Emahua%3C%2Fem%3E-based%20liquor%20has%20been%20in%20high%20demand%20traditionally.%20The%20Boudh%20Distillery%20Private%20Ltd%2C%20the%20flagship%20company%20of%20the%20group%2C%20has%20a%20near%20monopoly%20not%20only%20in%20Odisha%20but%20also%20in%20Jharkhand.%20It%20also%20supplies%20spirits%20for%20manufacturing%20IMFL%20in%20Odisha%2C%20where%20the%20group%20is%20said%20to%20account%20for%20about%2080%25%20of%20sales%20of%20spirits%20supplied%20to%20bottling%20plants%20in%20Berhampur%2C%20Khurda%2C%20Cuttack%2C%20Sambalpur%20and%20Rayagada.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702712886000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F16130459%2FScreenshot-2023-12-16-at-1.04.05%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-raids-cash-seizure-congress-mp-dhiraj-sahur-liquor-business-political-blame-game%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhiraj%20Sahu%2C%20in%20his%20first%20reaction%20to%20the%20raids%20on%20Friday%2C%20said%20the%20Rs%20350%20crore%20that%20was%20seized%20was%20the%20proceeds%20of%20his%20family%20liquor%20business%20and%20he%20can%20account%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fit-raids-cash-seizure-congress-mp-dhiraj-sahur-liquor-business-political-blame-game%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%227%20women%20injured%20in%20mortar%20shell%20explosion%20in%20restive%20northwest%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702712543000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106042384%2Cimgsize-735870.cms%22%