uns.%C2%A0This%20is%20the%20biggest%20margin%20of%20win%20(in%20terms%20of%20runs)%20in%20the%20history%20of%20women's%20Tests.%20%C2%A0The%20previous%20best%20was%20Sri%20Lanka's%20309-run%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20Colombo%20in%201998.%20The%20win%20was%20also%20Indian%20women's%20team's%20first%20over%20England%20at%20home.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20India's%20first%20win%20over%20England%20at%20home%20in%2015%20Tests%2C%20having%20beaten%20them%20in%20away%20games%20twice%20in%202014%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20big%20boost%20ahead%20of%20the%20one-off%20Test%20against%20Australia%20starting%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rajeshwari%20Gayakwad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64954-rajeshwari-shivanand-gayakwad-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERajeshwari%20Gayakwad%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20the%20final%20wicket%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTeamIndia%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TeamIndia%3C%2Fa%3E%20beat%20England%20by%20347%20runs%20in%20the%20only%20Test%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFantastic%20all-round%20performance%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINDvENG%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23INDvENG%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvNxqYw9CrL%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FvNxqYw9CrL%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20BCCI%20Women%20(%40BCCIWomen)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBCCIWomen%2Fstatus%2F1735909958456148339%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20match%2C%20Deepti%20Sharma%20played%20the%20enforcer's%20role%20to%20perfection%20for%20the%20second%20time%20in%20as%20many%20days%20as%20the%20dominant%20India%20Women%20scripted%20a%20historic%20347-run%20victory%20over%20England%20on%20the%20third%20day%20of%20the%20one-off%20Test%20on%20Saturday.%20India%20set%20in%20motion%20the%20hunt%20for%20triumph%20while%20declaring%20their%20second%20innings%20closed%20at%20the%20overnight%20score%20of%20186%20for%206%2C%20leaving%20England%20to%20climb%20a%20huge%20mountain%20of%20479%20runs%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20bowlers%20led%20by%20off-spinner%20Deepti%20Sharma%20(4%2F32)%20and%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pooja%20Vastrakar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117789-pooja-vastrakar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPooja%20Vastrakar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(3%2F23)%20then%20bundled%20out%20England%20for%20131%20to%20celebrate%20a%20victory%20which%20now%20stands%20as%20the%20biggest%20in%20terms%20of%20runs%20in%20the%20history%20of%20women's%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20last%20three%20days%20the%20Indians%20did%20not%20show%20any%20rust%20of%20not%20having%20played%20Test%20cricket%20in%20two%20years%2C%20and%20a%20first%20at%20home%20after%20nine%20years%2C%20while%20being%20at%20their%20ruthless%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20all%20that%20slew%20of%20records%2C%20the%20Harmanpreet%20Kaur-led%20side%20should%20thank%20Deepti%20(8-2-32-4)%20who%20was%20in%20her%20elements%20after%20that%20sensational%205%20for%20seven%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20as%20England%20lacked%20gumption%20to%20fight%20even%20on%20a%20pitch%20that%20appeared%20to%20be%20far%20more%20gentle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20long%20for%20the%20first%20breakthrough%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tammy%20Beaumont%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F116052-tammy-beaumont-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETammy%20Beaumont%3C%2Fa%3E%20(17)%20with%20pacer