England's%20misery%20continued%20when%20Wyatt%20edged%20a%20delivery%20to%20the%20first%20slip%20for%20Deepti's%20first%20wicket%20in%20the%20innings%20after%20making%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepti%20then%20had%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Amy%20Jones%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63017-amy-jones-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAmy%20Jones%3C%2Fa%3E%20(5)%20pulling%20one%20straight%20to%20short%20midwicket%2C%20and%20in%20her%20seventh%20over%20of%20the%20innings%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20hit%20the%20timber%20twice%20to%20dismiss%20Kate%20Cross%20(16)%20and%20Lauren%20Filer%20(0).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Deepti%20narrowly%20missed%20taking%2010%20wickets%20in%20the%20game%20to%20become%20the%20first%20Indian%20Women's%20player%20to%20do%20so%2C%20Rajeshwari%20Gayakwad%20(2%2F20)%20enjoyed%20some%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20left-arm%20spinner%20had%20her%20first%20success%20in%20the%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sophie%20Ecclestone%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117760-sophie-ecclestone-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESophie%20Ecclestone%3C%2Fa%3E%20(10)%20when%20the%20batter%20went%20for%20a%20sweep%20and%20missed%20to%20connect%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lauren%20Bell%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117815-lauren-bell-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELauren%20Bell%3C%2Fa%3E%20(8)%20was%20caught%20by%20Jemimah%20Rodrigues%20at%20silly%20point%20for%20the%20final%20wicket%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20perfect%20outing%20for%20India%20also%20given%20that%20all%20their%20debutants%20in%20the%20game%20-%20Shubha%20Satheesh%2C%20Rodrigues%20and%20Renuka%20-%20tasted%20success%2C%20but%20there%20also%20was%20a%20dampener%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Shubha%20missing%20the%20action%20on%20the%20second%20and%20the%20third%20day%20owing%20to%20a%20fractured%20finger.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%3C