20to%20have%20destroyed%20his%20and%20the%20others%20mobile%20phones%2C%20another%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20arrested%20accused%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20seven%20days'%20police%20custody.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702710240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fq4v4fauo_lok-sabha-breach_625x300_14_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-accused-considered-self-immolation-as-an-option-report-4684173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20five%20accused%20arrested%20in%20the%20December%2013%20Parliament%20security%20breach%20case%20have%20revealed%20that%20they%20explored%20self-immolation%20and%20distribution%20of%20pamphlets%20before%20settling%20on%20the%20plan%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha's%20chamber%20with%20smoke%20canisters.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-accused-considered-self-immolation-as-an-option-report-4684173%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-accused-considered-self-immolation-as-an-option-report-4684173%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-breach-accused-considered-self-immolation-as-an-option-report-4684173%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Covid-19%20sub-strain%20JN%201%20detected%20in%20Kerala%20woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702710183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106041525%2Cimgsize-37408.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fcovid-19-sub-strain-jn-1-detected-in-kerala-woman