ers-congress-8664366%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Congress%20denied%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20Simha%20said%20that%20stray%20dogs%20should%20be%20eliminated%20without%20any%20compassion%20after%20a%20pack%20of%20dogs%20mauled%20a%20five-year-old%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20stray%20dogs%20cannot%20be%20killed.%20Leaders%20from%20our%20own%20party%20create%20problems%20when%20stray%20dogs%20are%20killed.%20Even%20the%20media%20takes%20up%20incidents%20of%20attacks%20on%20stray%20dogs.%20While%20tigers%20and%20elephants%20have%20one%20or%20two%20litter%2C%20dogs%20have%20nearly%2010%20puppies.%20They%20should%20be%20eliminated%20without%20any%20compassion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fwell-eliminate-stray-dogs-if-media-keeps-silent-says-karnataka-bjp-mp-pratap-simha-8469644%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20as%20saying%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202019%2C%20Simha%20apologised%20to%20actor%20Prakash%20Raj%20for%20making%20%E2%80%9Cderogatory%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunwarranted%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20against%20him%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDear%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprakashraaj%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40prakashraaj%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20had%20posted%20a%20derogatory%20article%20against%20u%20n%20your%20family%20on%202%20%26amp%3B%203rd%20October%202017.%20However%20I%20understand%20these%20were%20unwarranted%20n%20hurtful.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20unequivocally%20withdraw%20n%20regret%20Twitter%20n%20FB%