tps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15230212%2FKT-15-Dec.00_48_06_06.Still003.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20highly%20regarded%20and%20well-thought-of%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20erred%20and%20cannot%20be%20proud%20of%20its%20Kashmir%20judgement%20but%2C%20instead%2C%20should%20review%20it.%20Justice%20Madan%20Lokur%20also%20described%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%20as%20complex%20and%20complicated%20adding%20it%E2%80%99s%20at%20least%20200%20pages%20too%20long.%C2%A0%20In%20his%20analysis%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20judgement%20and%20agreed%20the%20logic%20was%2C%20at%20times%2C%20if%20not%20often%2C%20%E2%80%9Cconvoluted%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%2040-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20made%20clear%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunhappy%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20way%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20what%20is%20popularly%20called%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20more%20unhappy%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20way%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20re-organisation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20constitutionally%20permissible%20under%20Article%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FmU5iUjf0Xsw%3Fsi%3Da83X7LLNevumT_fV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lokur%20made%20clear%20that%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20declared%20the%20use%20of%20Article%20367%20to%20interpret%20constituent%20assembly%20as%20legislative%20assembly%20as%20%3Cem%3Eultra%20vires%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20should%20have%20proceeded%20to%20strike%20down%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20was%20done%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20that%20reinterpretation.%20Not%20to%20do%20so%20was%20inconsistent%20with%20the%20logic%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20own%20arguement%2C%20he%20agreed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20re-organisation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20constitutionally%20proper%2C%20Justice%20Lokur%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20failed%20to%20fulfill%20its%20duty%20to%20look%20into%20this%20matter.%20He%20said%20it%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cerror%E2%80%9D%20not%20to%20decide%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lokur%20said%20one%20of%20the%20consequences%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20failing%20to%20determine%20the%20constitutionality%20of%20the%20re-organisation%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20that%20a%20precedent%20has%20been%20set%20which%20can%20be%20used%2C%20if%20the%20government%20should%20so%20wish%2C%20to%20re-organise%20other%20states%2C%20such%20as%20Bengal%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20reduce%20them%20to%20union%20territory%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Lokur%20agreed%20that%20another%20significant%20consequence%20is%20the%20impact%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20federalism%2C%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20previously%20deemed%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%20That%20means%20federalism%20cannot%20be%20amended.%20But%20now%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20given%20Parliament%20the%20power%20to%20re-organize%20a%20state%2C%20even%20without%20any%20recommendation%20from%20the%20state%20assembly.%20There%20could%20thus%20be%20a%20potential%20clash%20between%20the%20power%20of%20Parliament%20and%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20only%20giving%20you%20the%20big%20broad%20points%20of%20this%2040-minute%20interview.%20It%20is%20a%20tightly%20argued%20interview%2C%20and%20the%20conversation%20is%20often%20complex%20and%20complicated%2C%20and%20it%20requires%20great%20attentiveness.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20subject%20is%20not%20an%20easy%20one%20to%20follow%20and%20to%20understand%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judgement%20i.e.%20its%20logic%20and%20its%20inconsistencies%20is%20also%20deeply%20demanding%20of%20concentration%20and%20attentiveness.%20Rather%20than%20misconstrue%20and%20misrepresent%20what%20Justice%20Lokur%20has%20said%20I%20will%20leave%20you%20to%20hear%20this%20interview%20for%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%2C%20without%20doubt%2C%20the%20most%20comprehensive%20critique%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Kashmir%20judgement%20given%20by%20one%20of%20the%20most%20highly%20regarded%20former%20judges%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20If%20you%20wish%20to%20understand%20the%20judgement%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20its%20lapses%20and%20failings%2C%20I%20strongly%20recommend%20this%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20you%20will%20learn%20from%20this%20interview%20you%20will%20not%20have%20got%20from%20any%20earlier%20TV%20interview%20or%20newspaper%20interview%20or%2C%20possibly%2C%20from%20most%20commentaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702661707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15230212%2FKT-15-Dec.00_48_06_06.Still003.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-sc-erred-on-article-370-should-review-its-verdict-justice-madan-lokur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20the%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20said%20he%20was%20'unhappy'%20over%20court%20refusing%20to%20determine%20whether%20the%20re-organisation%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20constitutionally%20permissible%20under%20Article%203.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-sc-erred-on-article-370-should-review-its-verdict-justice-madan-lokur%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2220%20Tonnes%20of%20Oil-Soaked%20Soil%2C%207%2C000%20Litres%20of%20Affected%20Water%20Removed%3A%20TN%20Govt%20on%20Chennai%20Oil%20Spill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15214930%2FEffect-31.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EBengaluru%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20floods%20caused%20by%20Cyclone%20Michaung%2C%20Chennai%20is%20now%20grappling%20with%20an%20oil%20spill%20%E2%80%93%20the%20entire%20extent%20of%20which%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20assessed%2C%20per%20sources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20floodwaters%20caused%20by%20Cyclone%20Michaung%20swirled%20into%20homes%20and%20buildings%2C%20oil%20from%20the%20state-run%20refinery%20Chennai%20Petroleum%20Corporation%20Limited%20(CPCL)%20began%20leaking%20into%20Ko%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esasthalaiyar%20river%20in%20north%20Chennai%20via%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20and%20storm%20drains%20on%20December%204%2C%20per%20reports.%20The%20spill%20has%20now%20spread%20into%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20a%20crucial%20nursery%20for%20fish%20that%20local%20communities%20depend%20on%20for%20their%20livelihoods%2C%20before%20flowing%20out%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20environmentalists%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20state%20government%20departments%20have%20now%20sprung%20into%20action%20to%20stem%20the%20damages%2C%20local%20communities%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%2C%20as%20is%20the%20environment.%20The%20CPCL%20has%20employed%20local%20fishermen%20to%20conduct%20the%20clean%20up%20%E2%80%93%20but%20they%20are%20using%20their%20bare%20hands%20to%20scoop%20out%20the%20floating%20toxic%20oil%20in%20plastic%20mugs%2C%20and%20with%20no%20access%20to%20any%20protective%20gear.%20People%20in%20villages%20near%20the%20oil%20spill%20are%20experiencing%20numerous%20physical%20symptoms%20due%20to%20exposure%20to%20the%20toxic%20oil%20and%20air%2C%20such%20as%20skin%20and%20eye%20irritation%20and%20giddiness.%20Fisherfolk%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20fish%20kills%20have%20occurred%20and%20birds%20too%20have%20been%20affected%20in%20both%20the%20river%20and%20estuary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20reports%20submitted%20to%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(TNPCB)%20is%20investigating%20both%20the%20CPCL%20as%20well%20as%20another%20industry%20in%20the%20area%20%E2%80%93%20Toshiba-JSW%20%E2%80%93%20since%20the%20latter%20had%20also%20not%20%E2%80%9Chandled%E2%80%9D%20its%20used%20oil%20appropriately%20and%20could%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20oil%20spill%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20The%20TNPCB%20told%20the%20NGT%20on%20December%2014%20that%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20has%20been%20removed%20from%20the%20area%20so%20far%2C%20as%20have%207%2C000%20liters%20of%20oil%20mixed%20with%20water.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFirst%2C%20denial%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20first%2C%20there%20was%20denial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Cyclone%20Michaung%20struck%20Chennai%20in%20early%20December%2C%20the%20people%20of%20north%20Chennai%20near%20Ennore%20were%20also%20affected%3A%20water%20swirled%20into%20homes%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20electricity.%20The%20floods%2C%20however%2C%20also%20caused%20an%20oil%20leakage%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20The%20oil%20moved%20downstream%20from%20there%2C%20and%20into%20the%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river.%20From%20here%2C%20the%20oil%20slick%20traveled%20further%20downstream%20with%20the%20current%20and%20into%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20before%20trailing%20away%20into%20the%20sea.%20Media%20reported%20that%20the%20oil%20spill%20had%20reached%20residential%20areas%20including%20Thiruvotriyur%2C%20Nettukuppam%2C%20and%20Ennorekuppam.%20Though%20residents%20pointed%20fingers%20at%20the%20CPCL%20specifically%2C%20it%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-oil-spill-cyclone-michaung-after-cyclone-michaung-disaster-blame-game-erupts-over-chennai-oil-spill-4661962%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edenied%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20allegations.%20Precious%20time%20%E2%80%93%20that%20could%20have%20been%20used%20to%20immediately%20stem%20the%20oil%20spread%20%E2%80%93%20was%20thus%20lost.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15223658%2F2023_12_09_13_25_47_314-1-1-1024x770.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChennai%20oil%20spill.%20Photo%3A%20Suzhal%20Arivom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%207%2C%20the%20Southern%20Bench%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0wOS9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyMTI0MTY4NTMyMTQ4MTM5NjU3NDVhODhiMzIzNi5wZGY%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENational%20Green%20Tribunal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20took%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esuo%20moto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20cognisance%20of%20the%20issue%20after%20videos%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20emerged%20on%20visual%20media%2C%20and%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Pollution%20Control%20Board.%20The%20state%20government%20filed%20a%20report%20on%20December%209%20in%20response.%20The%20NGT%20noted%20in%20the%20report%20that%20the%20executive%20engineer%20of%20the%20Water%20Resources%20Department%20%E2%80%9Ccategorically%20stated%20that%20there%20is%20a%20serious%20threat%20to%20the%20life%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20marine%20organisms%2C%20aqua%20culture%20by%20loads%20of%20chemical%20effluents%20and%20waste%20oil%20spills%20which%20are%20clandestinely%20discharged%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20at%20various%20places%E2%80%9D%20including%20Kaatukuppam%20fishing%20village%20in%20Ennore.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwater%20surface%20was%20filled%20with%20a%20thick%20oily%20substance%20and%20it%20is%20visible%20all%20along%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20for%20more%20than%205%20Kms%20and%20also%20spread%20to%20Ennore%20Creek%20and%20Kosasthalaiyar%20River%20Mouth%20and%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CConsidering%20the%20health%20of%20the%20residents%2C%20and%20also%20the%20flora%20and%20fauna%20and%20aquatic%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20NGT%20also%20constituted%20a%20High-Level%20Committee%20comprising%20nine%20members%20including%20the%20Additional%20Chief%20Secretary%20to%20the%20government%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20TNPCB%2C%20district%20collectors%20of%20Chennai%20and%20Thiruvallur%20districts%20and%20the%20Director%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Fisheries%2C%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20It%20ordered%20that%20the%20Committee%20take%20immediate%20action%20to%20arrest%20the%20oil%20spread%2C%20and%20remove%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20affected%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOil%20spill%20spans%20across%2020%20sq%20km%20of%20sea%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20committee%20shall%20also%20get%20the%20damage%20assessment%20undertaken%20and%20arrive%20at%20the%20funds%20required%20for%20remediation%20as%20well%20as%20compensation%2C%20if%20any%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20green%20court%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20team%20of%20the%20state%20environment%20department%20led%20by%20the%20member-secretary%20of%20the%20TNPCB%20finally%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftamil-nadu%2F2023%2Fdec%2F12%2Fcpcl-faulted-for-oil-spill-in-ennore-2640789.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eidentified%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20CPCL%20as%20the%20source%20of%20the%20oil%20leakage%2C%20due%20to%20its%20poor%20management%20of%20storm%20water%20drains%20that%20are%20connected%20to%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal.%20Per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20has%20also%20asked%20the%20CPCL%20to%20implement%20urgent%20mitigation%20measures%20on%20priority%3B%20an%20impact%20study%20of%20affected%20fisherfolk%20families%20is%20underway%20and%20the%20state%20environment%20department%20is%20also%20assessing%20biodiversity%20loss%20in%20the%20area.%20On%20the%20same%20day%2C%20December%2011%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20also%20ordered%20the%20CPCL%20to%20identify%20%E2%80%9Chotspots%E2%80%9D%20of%20oil%20spillage%20in%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%2C%20Ennore%20estuary%20and%20the%20adjoining%20areas%20and%20take%20remedial%20measures%20immediately%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Ftn-pollution-cpcl-urgent-remedial-ennore-creek-oil-spillage-9064998%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Coast%20Guard%20has%20estimated%20that%20the%20oil%20spill%20has%20trailed%20into%20the%20sea%2C%20covering%20around%2020%20square%20kilometers%20of%20open%20water%2C%20activist%20and%20environmentalist%20Nityanand%20Jayaraman%2C%20of%20the%20Vettiver%20Collective%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20over%20phone.%20However%2C%20the%20extent%20%E2%80%93%20and%20impact%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20the%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river%20into%20which%20it%20leaked%20from%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%2C%20and%20the%20Ennore%20estuary%2C%20are%20still%20unassessed%2C%20Jayaraman%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20estuary%2C%20which%20also%20has%20patches%20of%20mangrove%20cover%2C%20is%20crucial%20for%20fishermen%20because%20it%20serves%20as%20a%20nursery%20for%20fish%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20sediments%20along%20the%20estuary%20have%20been%20coated%20with%20oil%2C%20he%20added.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20as%20good%20as%20running%20a%20bulldozer%20through%20the%20%5Bfish%5D%20nursery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20last%20oil%20spill%20that%20occurred%20off%20the%20Chennai%20coast%20%E2%80%93%20also%20off%20Ennore%2C%20but%20in%20the%20open%20sea%20%E2%80%93%20was%20in%20early%202017%2C%20when%20two%20oil%20tankers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20empty%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBW%20Maple%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20oil-loaded%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDawn%20Kancheepuram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20collided.%20However%2C%20the%202017%20spill%20is%20not%20comparable%20to%20the%20ongoing%20oil%20spill%20because%20the%20impacts%20caused%20in%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%20are%20very%20different%20when%20compared%20to%20that%20seen%20in%20the%20open%20sea%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPeople%20and%20the%20environment%20at%20risk%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFish%20kills%20have%20occurred%20in%20both%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%2C%20said%20R.L.%20Srinivasan%2C%20a%20fisherman%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20nearby%20Kaatukuppam%20fishing%20village%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20villages%20that%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20oil%20spill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oil%20spill%20lies%20thick%2C%20like%20a%20wad%20of%20four%20tissue%20papers%2C%20on%20the%20river%20and%20the%20estuary%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBirds%20in%20the%20area%20too%20have%20been%20coated%20with%20the%20oil%20and%20seem%20to%20be%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Febird.org%2Fhotspot%2FL22559793%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ee-Bird%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20global%20citizen%20science%20platform%20of%20bird%20listings%2C%20Ennore%20creek%20is%20home%20to%20many%20birds%20as%20well%20including%20the%20spot-billed%20pelican%20(a%20species%20that%20is%20listed%20as%20Near%20Threatened%20by%20the%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20of%20Threatened%20Species)%2C%20and%20migratory%20species%20such%20as%20the%20whimbrel%20and%20the%20wood%20sandpiper%2C%20which%20visit%20the%20area%20in%20winters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kosasthalaiyar%20now%20flows%20black%2C%20like%20a%20sewage%20drain%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Srinivasan.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOil%2C%20pushed%20by%20water%20currents%2C%20has%20also%20accumulated%20in%20thick%20layers%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20estuary%20where%20the%20currents%20are%20slower%2C%20both%20Srinivasan%20and%20Jayaraman%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20was%20also%20obvious%20right%20away%20was%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20the%20local%20communities%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20oil%20spill%20is%20just%20a%20five%20minute-walk%20from%20my%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20three%20days%20of%20the%20spill%20%E2%80%93%20with%20no%20electricity%20to%20boot%2C%20due%20to%20Cyclone%20Michaung%20%E2%80%93%20were%20a%20nightmare%2C%20he%20said.%20Most%20people%20in%20his%20village%20complained%20of%20eye%20and%20skin%20irritation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20giddiness%3B%20older%20people%20had%20wheezing%20and%20breathing%20issues%2C%20the%2043-year-old%20said.%20As%20the%20wind%20changed%20direction%2C%20there%20was%20some%20relief%2C%20Srinivsan%20said.%20But%20fishermen%20still%20have%20to%20wade%20through%20oil-covered%20waters%20to%20get%20their%20boats%20going.%20A%20thick%20layer%20of%20oil%20has%20also%20coated%20several%20boats%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20use%20them%20until%20they%20are%20cleaned.%20According%20to%20Jayaraman%2C%20boats%20belonging%20to%20four%20villages%20have%20been%20badly%20damaged%20this%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20anyway%2C%20there%20is%20no%20point%20going%20fishing%3B%20fish%20catch%20here%20reeks%20of%20oil.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%20protective%20gear%20for%20workers%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20see%20that%20oil%20leaks%20occur%20now%20and%20then%20from%20industries%20upstream%2C%20but%20this%20time%20it%20has%20been%20very%20different%20because%20of%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20flood%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20CPCL%20was%20issued%20orders%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20oil%2C%20they%20employed%20fishermen%20to%20do%20it%2C%20Srinivasan%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20that%20the%20CPCL%20knows%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20toxic%20oil%20on%20people%2C%20they%20do%20not%20let%20their%20staff%20handle%20it%20and%20instead%20make%20us%20do%20the%20dirty%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivasan%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20they%20did%20not%20give%20the%20fishermen%20any%20protective%20gear%20to%20use%20while%20doing%20this%20either.%20In%20this%20era%20of%20technology%2C%20how%20can%20you%20say%20there%20are%20no%20machines%20to%20do%20this%3F%20This%20is%20pathetic.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E2017%20buckets!%202023%20bathroom%20mugs!%20Its%20not%20ok%20to%20expose%20fishers%20who%20r%20victims%20of%20CPCLs%20oil%20pollution%20to%20more%20toxins%20in%20name%20of%20clean%20up.%20Is%20this%20SOP%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCMOTamilnadu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CMOTamilnadu%3C%2Fa%3E%20Pls%20insist%20on%20PPEs%2Ftraining%20for%20those%20engaged%20in%20spill%20response.%20No%20training.%20No%20safety.%20No%20dignity.%201%2Fn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOphDxBOEl7%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOphDxBOEl7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NityanandJayaraman%20(%40NityJayaraman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNityJayaraman%2Fstatus%2F1734515529707364717%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProtective%20gear%20is%20extremely%20important%20for%20any%20person%20engaging%20in%20cleaning%20up%20oil%20slicks%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%20Fishermen%20are%20scooping%20out%20the%20oil%20with%20plastic%20mugs%20using%20their%20bare%20hands.%20This%20is%20extremely%20dangerous%20for%20the%20people%20involved%2C%20Jayaraman%20said.%20Ideally%2C%20people%20engaged%20in%20the%20clean-up%20should%20be%20given%20the%20right%20masks%20and%20gloves%20and%20other%20protective%20gear%20but%20this%20has%20not%20happened%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20work%20also%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20up%20in%20shifts%20to%20decrease%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20that%20each%20worker%20is%20exposed%20to%20the%20toxic%20air%20and%20oil.%20Another%20crucial%20aspect%20is%20that%20the%20work%20should%20be%20done%20only%20after%20giving%20workers%20detailed%20briefings%20on%20how%20to%20go%20about%20it%20and%20what%20risks%20to%20avoid%20while%20conducting%20the%20clean-up%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20four%20ports%20in%20Chennai%2C%20no%20other%20city%20in%20India%20has%20so%20many%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jayaraman%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20four%20ports%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20expertise%20to%20deal%20with%20oil%20spills%20and%20have%20to%20have%20manual%20scavengers%20doing%20the%20job%3F%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20mechanical%20devices%20sucking%20it%20out%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FEnnoreOilSpill%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23EnnoreOilSpill%3C%2Fa%3E%20response%20is%20turning%20an%20environmental%20disaster%20into%20an%20Occupational%20Health%20disaster.%20Not%20the%20way%20to%20handle%20hazwaste.%20Lack%20of%20protocol%20%26amp%3B%20preparedness%20exposing%20workers%20to%20toxic%20%26amp%3B%20physical%20hazards.%20Wrong%20masks%2C%20no%20coveralls%2C%20no%20protocol.%20Dangerous%20ad-hocism.%201%2Fn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FzFguwvLChu%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FzFguwvLChu%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20NityanandJayaraman%20(%40NityJayaraman)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNityJayaraman%2Fstatus%2F1735300355804852297%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVisuals%20of%20flood%20rescue%20workers%20wading%20through%20the%20oil-laced%20waters%2C%20and%20videos%20of%20floods%20waters%20containing%20oil%20flowing%20into%20houses%20near%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%20were%20what%20prompted%20volunteers%20with%20Suzhal%20Arivom%2C%20a%20Chennai-based%20environmental%20group%2C%20to%20visit%20the%20area%20and%20look%20into%20it%2C%20said%20Deepak%20Venkatachalam%2C%20coordinator%20of%20the%20group.%20Their%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facrobat.adobe.com%2Fid%2Furn%3Aaaid%3Asc%3AAP%3A5cedbaa1-ebee-4e96-b2b6-e8bff18d2f69%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erapid%20assessment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20situation%20conducted%20in%20north%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20affected%20areas%20on%20December%209%20found%20that%20trails%20of%20oil%20were%20still%20coming%20from%20CPCL%20and%20that%20no%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20till%20then%20to%20arrest%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20oil%20into%20the%20river%2C%20estuary%20or%20sea%2C%20Venkatachalam%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98We%20need%20proper%20systems%20in%20place%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20is%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20learnt%20from%20the%20experience%20in%202017%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venkatachalam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202017%20oil%20spill%20off%20Ennore%20spread%20to%20the%20coast%20of%20southern%20Chennai%20and%20beyond%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20shores%20of%20Mahabalipuram%20and%20Kalpakkam%20%E2%80%93%20in%20less%20than%20a%20week%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20northeast%20monsoon%20is%20in%20play%2C%20and%20water%20currents%20along%20the%20shore%20run%20north%20to%20south%20during%20this%20time%2C%20the%20oil%20spill%20will%20swiftly%20move%20south%20and%20affect%20the%20shores%20in%20areas%20south%20of%20Ennore%20once%20it%20reaches%20the%20sea%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venkatachalam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20bodes%20bad%20news%20for%20the%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles%20that%20visit%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20coasts%20%E2%80%93%20including%20the%20Marina%20and%20Elliot%E2%80%99s%20beaches%20in%20Chennai%20%E2%80%93%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs%20there%2C%20according%20to%20Venkatachalam.%20The%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20classifies%20Olive%20Ridleys%20as%20%E2%80%9Cvulnerable%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20a%20decreasing%20trend%20in%20their%20numbers%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15224024%2F2023_12_09_15_30_03_654-1-1-1024x770.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-689396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EChennai%20oil%20spill.%20Photo%3A%20Suzhal%20Arivom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20oil%20booms%20%E2%80%93%20temporary%20floating%20barriers%20made%20of%20plastic%20that%20can%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20oil%20slick%20%E2%80%93%20are%20now%20in%20place%2C%20the%20delay%20may%20prove%20costly%2C%20Venkatachalam%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bdeploying%20booms%5D%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20scientific%20and%20cost-effective%20step%20to%20take%20to%20control%20the%20oil%20spread%20but%20it%20was%20delayed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Venkatachalam.%20%E2%80%9CAuthorities%20need%20to%20work%20towards%20a%20faster%20response%20time%20to%20avoid%20such%20disasters%20in%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20clean-up%20operation%20too%20has%20to%20be%20far%20more%20organized%20and%20efficient.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20paucity%20of%20people%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20oil%20spill%2C%20there%20is%20a%20definite%20drought%20of%20experts%20who%20know%20how%20to%20train%20people%2C%20help%20them%20understand%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20get%20this%20done%20without%20putting%20people%20in%20harm%E2%80%99s%20way%2C%20said%20Jayaraman.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20you%20respond%20to%20a%20disaster%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20disaster%20in%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EClean-up%20continues%3A%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20removed%2C%207%2C000%20liters%20of%20oil-laced%20water%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%2010%20days%20after%20the%20first%20traces%20of%20oil%20were%20spotted%20in%20Kosasthalaiyar%20river%20and%20Ennore%20creek%2C%20there%20is%20still%20no%20assessment%20of%20how%20much%20oil%20has%20spilled%20into%20the%20area%20and%20trailed%20to%20the%20sea.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchennai%2Fchennai-oil-spill-75-boats-300-personnel-mitigation-work-ennore-9067282%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2075%20boats%20and%20300%20people%20have%20now%20been%20pressed%20into%20the%20mitigation%20efforts%20to%20contain%20the%20oil%20spill%2C%20per%20a%20statement%20by%20Supriya%20Sahu%2C%20additional%20chief%20secretary%20of%20the%20Environment%2C%20Climate%20Change%20%26amp%3B%20Forests%20Department.%20Oil%20booms%20and%20an%20oil%20skimmer%20machine%20have%20also%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20creek%3B%20four%20more%20oil%20skimmers%20will%20also%20be%20deployed%20soon%2C%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivasan%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0xMi9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyNDQ1NzcxOTM0NjI1NDE2NTc5NDJjYjE4MmI2LnBkZg%3D%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epetitioned%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20Southern%20Bench%20of%20the%20NGT%20to%20ensure%20that%20authorities%20complete%20and%20clean%20all%20the%20impacted%20areas%20and%20dispose%20of%20the%20contaminated%20materials%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20Hazardous%20and%20Other%20Wastes%20(Management%20and%20Transboundary%20Movement)%20Rules%2C%202016%2C%20as%20well%20as%20provide%20necessary%20compensation%20to%20the%20impacted%20fishermen%20and%20restore%20the%20ecology%20and%20environment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20inspection%20by%20a%20team%20of%20the%20TNPCB%20revealed%20that%20they%20found%20%E2%80%9Coil-mixed%20and%20oil%20slick%20stretches%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20CPCL%20to%20Ennore%20Creek%2C%20along%20a%20distance%20of%2011%20km%2C%20the%20Board%20reported%20to%20the%20NGT%20on%20December%2011.%20Per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0xMi9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyNDQ1NzcxOTM0NjI1NDE2NTc5NDJjYjE4MmI2LnBkZg%3D%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20is%20also%20investigating%20another%20industry%20in%20the%20area%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20Toshiba-JSW%20%E2%80%93%20as%20it%20was%20found%20to%20have%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20properly%20handled%20the%20waste%20oil%2Fused%20oil%20which%20could%20have%20also%20caused%20discharge%20into%20the%20Buckingham%20Canal%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20order%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0xMi9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyNDQ1NzcxOTM0NjI1NDE2NTc5NDJjYjE4MmI2LnBkZg%3D%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20December%2012%2C%20the%20NGT%20noted%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Government%20and%20CPCL%20take%20care%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20health%20and%20safety%20of%20the%20fishermen%20who%20have%20been%20pressed%20into%20service%20%E2%80%9Cby%20supplying%20safety%20gears%20like%20gloves%2C%20masks%20and%20any%20other%20safety%20equipment%20required%20for%20the%20same%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGT%20has%20also%20ordered%20the%20Fisheries%20Department%20to%20file%20a%20detailed%20report%20on%20the%20mass%20fish%20mortality%20recorded%20in%20the%20river%20and%20Ennore%20creek.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20for%20the%20Fisheries%20Department%20to%20tell%20when%20it%20would%20be%20appropriate%20for%20fishermen%20to%20enter%20into%20the%20sea%2Fbackwaters%20as%20this%20oil%20spillage%20is%20reported%20to%20have%20affected%20the%20livelihood%20of%20the%20fishermen%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NGT%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20state%20government%20to%20list%20the%20measures%20that%20they%20have%20taken%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20interfering%20with%20fisher%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%20when%20the%20oil%20spill%20made%20it%20impossible%20for%20fisherfolk%20to%20head%20to%20the%20sea%20after%20the%20cyclone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20December%2014%2C%20TNPCB%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgreentribunal.gov.in%2Fgen_pdf_test.php%3Ffilepath%3DL25ndF9kb2N1bWVudHMvbmd0L2Nhc2Vkb2Mvb3JkZXJzL0NIRU5OQUkvMjAyMy0xMi0xNC9jb3VydHMvMS9kYWlseS8xNzAyNjMwMTMxNDY1MzIzNzI0NjU3YzEyZjM2OGQ1ZC5wZGY%3D%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20the%20NGT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20December%2014%20that%20about%2020%20tonnes%20of%20oil-soaked%20soil%20has%20been%20removed%20so%20far.%20It%20also%20submitted%20that%20around%207%2C000%20liters%20of%20oil%20and%20water%20has%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20waters%20in%20Ennore%20creek.%20So%20far%2C%2075%20boats%2C%20one%20oil%20skimmer%2C%20and%20four%20JCBs%20are%20currently%20being%20used%20in%20the%20clean%20up%20process%3B%209%2C900%20absorbent%20pads%20have%20also%20been%20used%20to%20absorb%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20water%20surface%2C%20the%20TNPCB%20reported%20to%20the%20NGT.%20Apart%20from%20using%20oil%20skimmers%2C%20ejectors%2C%20gully%20suckers%20as%20well%20as%20bio-dispersal%20sprays%2C%20the%20CPCL%20has%20pressed%20into%20service%20a%20Chennai-based%20agency%20that%20has%20expertise%20in%20oil%20spill%20management%20to%20clear%20the%20oil%20from%20the%20water%20surface%3B%20the%20company%20is%20also%20supposedly%20cleaning%20up%20homes%20and%20schools.%20The%20NGT%20has%20ordered%20the%20CPCL%20to%20complete%20the%20entire%20cleanup%20work%20before%20December%2017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20complete%20the%20work%20expeditiously%2C%20it%20is%20suggested%20that%20CPCL%20should%20deploy%20more%20machinery%2C%20material%20and%20personnel%20in%20the%20said%20operation%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20experts%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NGT%E2%80%99s%20Southern%20Bench%20of%20Justice%20Pushpa%20Sathyanarayana%20and%20Expert%20Member%20K.%20Satyagopal%20noted%20in%20the%20order%20dated%20December%2014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20deployed%20a%20task%20force%20to%20study%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20Olive%20Ridley%20turtles%20in%20the%20area%2C%20while%20IIT%20Madras%20will%20conduct%20a%20study%20to%20assess%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20oil%20spill%20on%20the%20environment%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20NGT%20will%20now%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20December%2018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702661320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F15214930%2FEffect-31.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F20-tonnes-of-oil-soaked-soil-7000-litres-of-affected-water-removed-tn-govt-on-chennai-oil-spill%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mitigation%20efforts%20are%20still%20on%20to%20remove%20remaining%20oil%2C%20but%20they%20are%20proving%20inadequate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F20-tonnes-of-oil-soaked-soil-7000-litres-of-affected-water-removed-tn-govt-on-chennai-oil-spill%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22General%20Atlantic%20pares%2010%25%20stake%20in%20KFin%20Technologies%20for%20Rs%20851%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702660835000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F02%2Ffull%2F1698864209-2418.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-atlantic-pares-10-stake-in-kfin-technologies-for-rs-851-cr-123121501331_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shares%20were%20disposed%20of%20at%20an%20average%20price%20of%20Rs%20500.50%20apiece%2C%20taking%20the%20transaction%20value%20to%20Rs%20850.85%20crore%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-atlantic-pares-10-stake-in-kfin-technologies-for-rs-851-cr-123121501331_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-co