ities%20in%20Kashmir%20disallowed%20the%20congregational%20prayers%20at%20the%20historic%20mosque%20Jamia%20Masjid%20in%20Srinagar%20city%20for%20the%20tenth%20consecutive%20Friday%20without%20any%20official%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Anjuman%20Auqaf%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%2014th-century%20mosque%2C%20said%20that%20authorities%20in%20Srinagar%20also%20put%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chief%20Mirwaiz%20Umar%20Farooq%20under%20house%20arrest%20on%20Friday%2C%20December%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20chief%20cleric%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20delivers%20the%20main%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20before%20the%20congregational%20Friday%20prayers%20and%20on%20other%20important%20religious%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20reason%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20authorities%20for%20these%20restrictions%20and%20curbs%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20managing%20body%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20claims%20of%20so-called%20normalcy%20by%20rulers%20fall%20flat%20by%20such%20anti-people%20measures%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%20said%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20denouncing%20the%20curbs%20while%20accusing%20the%20authorities%20of%20allegedly%20targeting%20Jamia%20Masjid%20%E2%80%9Cagain%20and%20again%20%E2%80%A6.%20to%20cause%20grief%20to%20Muslims%20of%20the%20valley%20and%20show%20them%20their%20place%20in%20%E2%80%98naya%20Kashmir%E2%80%99.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlluding%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20Centre%2C%20Mirwaiz%20said%20that%20the%20authorities%20should%20%E2%80%9Cstop%20playing%20with%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Muslims%C2%A0%C2%A0and%20let%20them%20offer%20prayers%20in%20their%20mosques%20without%20hindrance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%E2%80%99s%20silence%20and%20endurance%20of%20brazen%20attacks%20on%20their%20religious%20rights%20should%20not%20be%20mistaken%20as%20their%20weakness%20to%20respond%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%202002%20dialogue%20on%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20with%20Pakistan%20initiated%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20this%20year%2C%20after%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chief%20was%20released%20from%20%E2%80%98house%20arrest%E2%80%99%20and%20allowed%20to%20deliver%20the%20Friday%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20in%20Nowhatta%20locality%20of%20downtown%20Srinagar%20which%20used%20to%20be%20a%20separatist%20hotbed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20at%20the%20mosque%20had%20triggered%20emotional%20scenes%20as%20he%20stood%20to%20address%20the%20worshippers%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20stripped%20of%20its%20special%20status.%20On%20the%20pulpit%2C%20the%20Hurriyat%20leader%20broke%20down%20and%20struggled%20to%20hold%20back%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20mosque%2C%20which%20is%20thronged%20by%20thousands%20of%20Muslims%20on%20important%20religious%20occasions%2C%20has%20since%20remained%20largely%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20worshippers%20on%20Fridays%20with%20authorities%20citing%20alleged%20fears%20of%20law-and-order%20disturbances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMirwaiz%20delivered%20his%20sermon%20at%20the%20mosque%20on%20two%20Fridays%20out%20of%2013%20since%20his%20release%20on%20September%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20officials%20have%20reportedly%20justified%20the%20closure%20of%20Jamia%20Masjid%2C%20the%20managing%20body%20of%20the%20mosque%20has%20accused%20the%20authorities%20of%20infringing%20on%20the%20religious%20rights%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20close%20the%20historical%20mosque%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20upheld%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20August%205%2C%202019%20decision%20of%20reading%20down%20Article%20370%20and%20downgrading%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20into%20two%20Union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20authorities%20disallowed%20Friday%20prayers%20at%20the%20mosque%20amid%20reported%20apprehensions%20that%20worshippers%20might%20stage%20protests%20or%20take%20out%20demonstrations%20in%20support%20of%20Gaza%20and%20against%20Israel%20by%20sealing%20the%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20some%20Kashmir-based%20preachers%20also%20accused%20the%20local%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Centre%2C%20of%20%E2%80%9Cmuting%E2%80%9D%20the%20mention%20of%20Palestine%20in%20their%20sermons%20on%20Fridays%20at%20the%20mosques%20across%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20%E2%80%9Cverbal%20instructions%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20authorities%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Wakf%20Board%2C%20which%20runs%20shrines%20across%20the%20Union%20territory%2C%20some%20preachers%20alleged%20that%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20%E2%80%9Cavoid%20mentioning%20the%20Palestine%20issue%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20annual%20festival%20of%20a%20prominent%20Sufi%20saint%20at%20a%20shrine%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecurity%20personnel%20were%20also%20monitoring%20the%20sermons%20being%20made%20and%20had%20also%20conveyed%20against%20arousing%20passions%20over%20the%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20two%20anonymous%20preachers%20as%20saying%20on%20November%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20sporadic%20protests%20broke%20out%20in%20Kashmir%20parts%20over%20a%20%E2%80%98blasphemous%E2%80%99%20social%20media%20post%20by%20a%20student%20at%20the%20prestigious%20National%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20in%20Srinagar%20with%20a%20top%20police%20official%20claiming%20that%20a%20conspiracy%20was%20being%20hatched%20%E2%80%9Cacross%20the%20border%E2%80%9D%20to%20use%20anger%20against%20the%20post%20for%20%E2%80%9Cother%20things%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702655439000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A